{"tid":1692294,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［戰略討論］分化CCTVB新聞部 記者vs主播","createTime":"2019-11-04T04:15:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T07:13:56.000Z","uid":190396,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d8c2c5b7dbdfd4bfe2a14165840d3e7865832ef0","tid":1692294,"uid":190396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T04:15:16.000Z","msg":"見到出邊有Post傾梗好唔好屌CCTVB記者，所以就想講下，其實<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記者</span></span> 同 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">主播</span></strong></span> 係完全唔同嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本身識人係做梗前線記者，呢幾個月都食過幾次TG。之前同佢傾過計，本身好多前線記者根本就睇唔起班主播，覺得佢地日日係廠到做讀稿機，唔洗出出邊跑新聞做扒。班主播頂盡都係寫下天文台D稿咁。<br />\n<br />\n好多Post都講過CCTVB d前線記者本身都係黃，純粹份稿入左廠之後改到變左另一回事。所以，真係唔好針對前線記者。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實做得主播既，十個有九個都純粹當CCTVB係踏腳石，純粹貪有得日日出鏡增加曝光率。佢地最終目的都係跳去大公司/政府機構做PR，大家去wiki search下就知大量記者都係辭職走去做PR。而D公司都成日請前記者/主播做PR，貪佢地識應付班傳媒。<br />\n<br />\n所以大家有冇諗過我地可以斷左班讀字機既後路，要佢地成世都係cctvb做讀字機<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地可以做既野，除左印曬CCTVB d screen cap + 佢地個樣黎做文宣之外，可以考慮下同其他公司講：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果請左CCTVB既主播做PR既話，我地就自自然然唔會幫襯你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁樣一黎可以比到壓力CCTVB，D主播走曬既話袁花唔知會唔會出番黎做主播呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 二黎可以阻止其他人入去CCTVB做主播<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家覺得點<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59291762cd01da211f117a4c1e1f6f3efda7d8dc","tid":1692294,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T04:16:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但我喺現場見過tvb冼志喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"b927191539f76ac0a5e094c0f39ab9d38753c5a4","tid":1692294,"uid":112581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T04:17:50.000Z","msg":"拆佢機啦<br />\n仲分化"},{"pid":"c2b356e7c08b4b90912ec370232425fce1b8e4a0","tid":1692294,"uid":8014,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T04:18:50.000Z","msg":"搞左5個月<br />\n有良心嗰d辭晒職啦<br />\n淨係嗰d 咪就係影人大頭影人換裝篤灰狗<br />\n無無辜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d62837d18e8a8cfa8393905274042766d86b986f","tid":1692294,"uid":129134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:13:56.000Z","msg":"樓主同你個朋友講<br />\n唔將新聞部編輯、採主、剪片篤出嚟<br />\n小心比人關照<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}